</P></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umacfudd.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Macfudd</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/20/01 10:37:50 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: solists icy wand</span><hr size=1> I'm bound outside Kurn's Tower now with my Wizard on Zebuxoruk.  I went there at 22 when I finally trivialed out cured silk and had had enough of hunting Crag Spiders.  I've been there about 3 weeks now and I'm half way to 24.  I don't mind that it is taking ages, I'm making slow but steady xp.  My dodge is rocketing up, and I'm getting decent loot moneywise.  To break the monotony I port into Greater Faydark every few days to sell banded and either smith or get cooking stuff to take back with me.  <br>
Oh, from what I have heard the wand drops of Burynai Excavators and Lesser Iceboned Skeletons, but it is ultra rare so be prepared for the long haul.  But if you could convince a few friends to go with you it is a nice zone to hunt once you know your way around. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umastuqe.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mastuqe</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/21/01 1:53:24 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: solists icy wand</span><hr size=1> Just so you know guys,Verant has this place sealed up nice and tight. Mobs only drop loot,if you get experience from them,when they spawn,so say,lvl 25 camps IBC,he has better chance of getting drop then a 50+ wizzie. It is the same with the wand. best thing to do,is run around,kill a spawn,then wait outside. Or else you will be killing pokeymans forever! Just a piece of advice..seen a few wands by doing so with a pet class alt who is 50+. Also about the dagger,it is hard to sell,but usually I snuck it in with trades just to save myself a few k. Oh well g'luck all <p><table border="0" width="111">
