</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ueindyinromenril.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Eindyin Romenril</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/21/01 2:29:20 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://eindyin.homestead.com/files/einphoto.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: solists icy wand</span><hr size=1> I've spent many many hours on various alts in Kurn's and only saw one drop once for a level 45 necro... Bought one the other day in EC for 400pp <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   It's pretty much useless to me, but i've always wanted one.  Works ok for killing the occasional aggroed mummy in Sro. <p><Font color=red>Eindyin Romenril<br>
