Ayonae Ro server</font></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uspankda.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Spankda</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/21/01 7:30:12 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: solists icy wand</span><hr size=1> I don't have any valuable information to add about the drop on this thing.<br>
<br>
I traded an FBSS for the wand plus 500pp from a monk who said, at the time, he got it off a burnai.<br>
<br>
I don't know because now he doesn't remember.<br>
<br>
However, on the  usefulness, I can say that I love this stinking wand.  I would marry this wand, but the relationship would be a cold one.<br>
<br>
I can not tell you how often I have used this wand to finish a mob and I'm OOM and Harvest is used.  Folks, my attack is like 21/100.  I have absolutely zero melee skills that work on blue mobs. <br>
<br>
I have no desire to up such skills.  I am a wizard, not a melee class.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uvahrakjlorjallag.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vahrak Jlorjallag</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/21/01 10:39:57 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: solists icy wand</span><hr size=1> Personally I find this wand pretty ghey....Ciladan conned me into buying his and then he got the Al'Kabor staff...hmmm...wish i could trade him ...<br>
<br>
oh well<br>
<br>
the long cast and low dmg make this wand lame...<br>
<br>
Vahrak Jlorjallag <br>
Sorcerer -- The Nameless <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uvermil.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vermil</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/21/01 10:58:16 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: solists icy wand</span><hr size=1> I got mine some time back. I took my lv 45 Necro in there. I had 3 reasons to be there.<br>
<br>
1. Collect bone chips<br>
2. Look for a Solist Icy Wand for my Twink<br>
3. Look for an Iksar Beserker Club<br>
<br>
I spent about 12 hours total in the tower, roaming the stables area letting my pet beat up on EVERYTHING. I cast root occasionally to stop runners. I secured myself about 18 stacks of bone chips, over 100 plat in gold and gems, one Solist Icy Wand and no IBC.<br>
<br>
The wand dropped off a Buryani and it was actually the last thing i killed before I was about to log.<br>
<br>
I also scored a bunch of Buryani armour (great to hand to newbies - although the +2 STR and +2 WIS on the boots may suit another twink <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  ). Also i picked up loads of Reinforced Rhino armor that I gave to noobs.<br>
<br>
I like my wand - although its effectiveness is wearing off as I gain levels. I got mine at lv 17 and it was great for a finisher in Oasis on the crocs. No mana? No problem, 38DD every 4 seconds. Great for runners and it frees up another spell slot.<br>
<br>
I even used it in Sol A last night - I got my Heart of Fire for my SoTF last night - I was with a Druid friend, I went OOM but was still able to help out a bit, thanks to my Wand. <br>
<br>
At a later level, I'll give it to a Guildmate or sell it. It is a nice weapon for levels 1-30. <p>Vermil Darkmire<BR>

<i>Lv 45 Dark Elf Necromancer</i><br>

Whammy<br>

<i>Level 30 Gnome Wizard</i></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessage?topicID=6453.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessage?topicID=6382.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=6440.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.threadControl?topicID=6440.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=6440.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=6440.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1">General Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm3">Trade Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm4">Rant Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm8">Mob Dropped Spells<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm10">Class Balance & Class Bugs<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm22">Out of Mana<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm27">PVP Forum<opti